Ah, cut it out.

1393
01:17:15,897 --> 01:17:17,864
Ash!

1394
01:17:17,899 --> 01:17:19,832
Everybody OK?

1395
01:17:19,868 --> 01:17:20,833
And the soul-heart?

1396
01:17:24,973 --> 01:17:26,940
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1397
01:17:32,981 --> 01:17:33,913
[GRUNTS]

1398
01:17:33,949 --> 01:17:36,916
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1399
01:17:36,952 --> 01:17:39,919
[CLANKING]

1400
01:17:39,955 --> 01:17:42,555
[GRUNTS]

1401
01:17:52,901 --> 01:17:54,567
Magearna, we're here.

1402
01:17:59,608 --> 01:18:01,808
[ALL GASP]

1403
01:18:01,843 --> 01:18:05,578
MEOWTH: It's heart
is still broken.

1404
01:18:05,614 --> 01:18:07,747
Sure it can move
and all that stuff.

1405
01:18:07,782 --> 01:18:14,721
But now, Magearna's voice,
I can't hear it at all.

1406
01:18:14,756 --> 01:18:16,723
[GRUNTS]

1407
01:18:18,960 --> 01:18:20,727
[ALL SIGH]

1408
01:18:20,795 --> 01:18:21,728
[CLANKING]

1409
01:18:21,763 --> 01:18:22,528
[ALL GASPING]

1410
01:18:28,737 --> 01:18:29,736
Oh, no.

1411
01:18:29,771 --> 01:18:34,407
The fortress is set to
fall onto Nebel Plateau.

1412
01:18:34,442 --> 01:18:35,642
Can it be stopped?

1413
01:18:35,677 --> 01:18:38,711
It can't it looks like
the control system is out.

1414
01:18:38,747 --> 01:18:42,348
All because of Alva.

1415
01:18:42,384 --> 01:18:44,384
And even if we were
able to escape--

1416
01:18:56,798 --> 01:18:59,365
Isn't there any way at all?

1417
01:18:59,401 --> 01:19:00,767
We can't change course.

1418
01:19:00,802 --> 01:19:03,302
The only way would be
to explode the fortress

1419
01:19:03,338 --> 01:19:05,705
into a pile of dust.

1420
01:19:05,740 --> 01:19:09,409
Explosions are my specialty.

1421
01:19:09,444 --> 01:19:10,576
Hold on.

1422
01:19:10,612 --> 01:19:11,444
You're out of water.

1423
01:19:14,649 --> 01:19:19,585
Part of the fortress runs on
steam so it has water tanks.

1424
01:19:19,621 --> 01:19:22,288
Volcanion, I'll take you there.

1425
01:19:22,323 --> 01:19:24,290
Please do.

1426
01:19:24,325 --> 01:19:27,360
Everybody, wait on my
sister's flying machine.

1427
01:19:27,395 --> 01:19:28,628
I'm going with you.

1428
01:19:28,663 --> 01:19:29,629
Pika ka.

1429
01:19:35,370 --> 01:19:36,335
Over here!

1430
01:19:39,474 --> 01:19:41,274
I can smell water.

1431
01:19:43,712 --> 01:19:45,645
[GROANING]

1432
01:19:47,348 --> 01:19:50,316
This thing is really stuck.

1433
01:19:50,351 --> 01:19:51,350
I've got it.

1434
01:19:51,386 --> 01:19:52,752
Go for it, Pikachu.

1435
01:19:52,787 --> 01:19:53,720
Irontail!

1436
01:19:53,755 --> 01:19:55,354
Pika!

1437
01:19:55,390 --> 01:19:56,589
Ah, pika!

1438
01:20:01,629 --> 01:20:02,462
Hey, thanks.

1439
01:20:02,497 --> 01:20:04,664
[GROANING]

1440
01:20:09,370 --> 01:20:10,336
It's moving.

1441
01:20:17,378 --> 01:20:18,377
All right.

1442
01:20:18,413 --> 01:20:19,345
Yeah!

1443
01:20:34,395 --> 01:20:36,262
Excuse me.

1444
01:20:36,297 --> 01:20:37,697
You said your name
was Ash, right?

1445
01:20:37,732 --> 01:20:39,265
That's right.

1446
01:20:39,300 --> 01:20:41,634
I've been acting
like such a fool,

1447
01:20:41,669 --> 01:20:45,404
spending so long shutting
myself up in my lab.

1448
01:20:45,440 --> 01:20:51,377
That's why Alva had such an
easy time tricking me that way.

1449
01:20:51,412 --> 01:20:53,646
You know what I think?

1450
01:20:53,681 --> 01:20:57,350
You should head out on your
own journey with a Pokemon.

1451
01:20:57,385 --> 01:20:58,351
Huh?

1452
01:20:58,386 --> 01:20:59,352
Mm-hmm.

1453
01:20:59,387 --> 01:21:01,354
Pika te.

1454
01:21:01,389 --> 01:21:02,321
[CRASH]

1455
01:21:02,357 --> 01:21:03,322
[GASPS]

1456
01:21:13,434 --> 01:21:14,400
[CRASH]

1457
01:21:23,545 --> 01:21:25,511
[PANTING]

1458
01:21:29,784 --> 01:21:30,883
Volcanion?

1459
01:21:30,919 --> 01:21:35,454
Say, perhaps I should create
an explosion right here.

1460
01:21:35,490 --> 01:21:37,456
ASH: It is the center
of the fortress

1461
01:21:37,492 --> 01:21:39,358
so I do think it
would be effective.

1462
01:21:39,394 --> 01:21:41,727
But then you won't
be able to escape.

1463
01:21:41,763 --> 01:21:43,462
Vita vio.

1464
01:21:43,498 --> 01:21:45,498
Yeah, that's the truth.

1465
01:21:45,533 --> 01:21:48,634
You said you're powerful enough
to level a mountain, right?

1466
01:21:48,670 --> 01:21:51,437
So why not follow the plan
and blow it up from outside?

1467
01:21:51,472 --> 01:21:52,805
Hmm.

1468
01:21:52,841 --> 01:21:54,807
Agreed.

1469
01:21:54,843 --> 01:21:56,475
We should all go back together.

1470
01:21:56,511 --> 01:21:57,443
Yeah.

1471
01:21:57,478 --> 01:21:58,377
Pika!

1472
01:21:58,413 --> 01:22:00,379
[CRASH]

1473
01:22:00,415 --> 01:22:01,347
Let's hurry.

1474
01:22:08,556 --> 01:22:09,455
[CRASH]

1475
01:22:09,490 --> 01:22:10,456
[ALL GASP]

1476
01:22:23,805 --> 01:22:25,471
OK, Volcanion.

1477
01:22:25,506 --> 01:22:26,672
Go get them!

1478
01:22:26,708 --> 01:22:27,506
[GRUNTS]

1479
01:22:38,586 --> 01:22:40,519
Get on board after the blast.

1480
01:22:40,555 --> 01:22:42,321
All right.

1481
01:22:42,357 --> 01:22:43,656
Just go!

1482
01:22:43,691 --> 01:22:45,658
[ALL MOANING]

1483
01:22:49,731 --> 01:22:50,663
CHYMIA: Volcanion!

1484
01:22:56,704 --> 01:22:57,536
No!

1485
01:22:57,572 --> 01:22:59,338
You can't do that!

1486
01:23:04,579 --> 01:23:05,811
[GRUNTS]

1487
01:23:15,790 --> 01:23:18,758
Well, I'm going
out with a bang.

1488
01:23:18,793 --> 01:23:20,393
Time to blast!

1489
01:23:29,804 --> 01:23:34,473
Magearna, I couldn't
protect you.

1490
01:23:34,509 --> 01:23:36,442
Forgive me.

1491
01:23:36,477 --> 01:23:39,478
[ROARING]

1492
01:23:46,421 --> 01:23:47,553
Volcanion.

1493
01:23:47,588 --> 01:23:50,323
[HIGH PITCHED SOUND]

1494
01:23:56,464 --> 01:23:59,398
[EXPLOSION]

1495
01:24:18,753 --> 01:24:21,387
You lied to us.

1496
01:24:21,422 --> 01:24:24,390
You said we'd all
go back together!

1497
01:24:24,425 --> 01:24:25,558
Heego bego.

1498
01:24:49,450 --> 01:24:51,517
Magearna?

1499
01:24:51,552 --> 01:24:54,320
The Nebel Plateau
Pokemon are safe.

1500
01:24:54,355 --> 01:24:57,490
Volcanion protected them.

1501
01:24:57,525 --> 01:24:59,592
I wish you could
hear what I'm saying.

1502
01:24:59,627 --> 01:25:02,395
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1503
01:25:07,402 --> 01:25:09,368
[ALL WHIMPERING]

1504
01:25:12,607 --> 01:25:14,373
[PURRING]

1505
01:25:18,613 --> 01:25:20,379
[CRYING]

1506
01:25:20,415 --> 01:25:22,548
[GASPS]

1507
01:25:22,583 --> 01:25:25,351
[ALL WHIMPERING]

1508
01:25:28,589 --> 01:25:30,556
[GASPING]

1509
01:25:37,432 --> 01:25:38,397
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1510
01:25:38,433 --> 01:25:39,598
Look at the mist.

1511
01:25:39,634 --> 01:25:40,599
[GENTLE MUSIC]

1512
01:25:47,575 --> 01:25:48,541
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1513
01:25:57,385 --> 01:25:58,350
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1514
01:26:02,390 --> 01:26:03,355
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1515
01:26:22,410 --> 01:26:24,343
[BEEPING]

1516
01:26:28,349 --> 01:26:29,515
[GRUNTING]

1517
01:26:29,550 --> 01:26:31,517
[BEEPING]

1518
01:26:31,552 --> 01:26:33,519
[ALL EXCLAIMING]

1519
01:26:34,522 --> 01:26:36,288
Magearna.

1520
01:26:36,324 --> 01:26:39,291
[BEEPING]

1521
01:26:45,466 --> 01:26:47,466
Chesnah.

1522
01:26:47,502 --> 01:26:48,434
Chesnah.

1523
01:26:52,640 --> 01:26:53,606
[GRUNTING]

1524
01:26:53,641 --> 01:26:55,608
[BEEPING]

1525
01:26:56,611 --> 01:26:58,377
[GRUNTS]

1526
01:27:00,414 --> 01:27:02,581
[GROANS]

1527
01:27:02,617 --> 01:27:05,551
[ALL GASP]

1528
01:27:05,586 --> 01:27:07,620
Volcanion, hang in there.

1529
01:27:09,590 --> 01:27:10,523
Volcanion?

1530
01:27:14,762 --> 01:27:16,395
Oh.

1531
01:27:16,430 --> 01:27:18,364
Pika.

1532
01:27:18,399 --> 01:27:21,300
[WHIMPERING]

1533
01:27:32,613 --> 01:27:33,512
[GASPS]

1534
01:27:33,548 --> 01:27:36,282
[SQUEAKING]

1535
01:27:36,317 --> 01:27:38,617
[GASPING]

1536
01:27:40,521 --> 01:27:42,354
[SNEEZES]

1537
01:27:42,390 --> 01:27:44,456
[POKEMON SCREAM]

1538
01:27:47,628 --> 01:27:49,762
I told you not to do that.

1539
01:27:49,797 --> 01:27:52,364
[POKEMON SQUEAKING]

1540
01:27:54,368 --> 01:27:57,436
You, you're still here?

1541
01:27:57,471 --> 01:28:00,539
I said I want to
protect Pokemon, right?

1542
01:28:00,575 --> 01:28:02,541
I would never tell a lie.

1543
01:28:02,577 --> 01:28:04,343
Be davi ya!

1544
01:28:04,378 --> 01:28:09,248
[CHUCKLES] All of you.

1545
01:28:09,283 --> 01:28:10,482
You know what?

1546
01:28:10,518 --> 01:28:12,418
Huh?

1547
01:28:12,453 --> 01:28:16,622
I'm going to make you all
honorary Nebel Plateau Pokemon.

1548
01:28:16,657 --> 01:28:18,490
Honorary Pokemon.

1549
01:28:18,526 --> 01:28:21,293
Hey, I think that
sounds really cool.

1550
01:28:21,329 --> 01:28:24,563
Yeah, I want to be one!

1551
01:28:24,599 --> 01:28:26,498
Yeah, right, Squishy?

1552
01:28:26,534 --> 01:28:27,666
Mm-hmm.

1553
01:28:27,702 --> 01:28:29,635
Well, I'm happy to accept.

1554
01:28:29,670 --> 01:28:31,303
It's a real honor.

1555
01:28:31,339 --> 01:28:32,671
[ALL LAUGHING]

1556
01:28:40,615 --> 01:28:42,581
Hey, electric nuisance.

1557
01:28:42,617 --> 01:28:43,682
Pika.

1558
01:28:43,718 --> 01:28:46,452
Your friend, Ash,
he always seems to be

1559
01:28:46,487 --> 01:28:48,520
getting himself into trouble.

1560
01:28:48,556 --> 01:28:49,655
Pika?

1561
01:28:49,690 --> 01:28:53,659
Take extra good care of him.

1562
01:28:53,694 --> 01:28:56,462
Pika, me gatsu.

1563
01:28:56,497 --> 01:28:57,696
[LAUGHS]

1564
01:29:18,486 --> 01:29:21,453
[MUSIC PLAYING]

1565
01:29:32,500 --> 01:29:35,501
WOMAN (SINGING):
One of a kind, forged

1566
01:29:35,536 --> 01:29:44,576
of steel from a beautiful
night with a mighty heart,

1567
01:29:44,612 --> 01:29:49,548
drove men apart.

1568
01:29:49,583 --> 01:29:56,722
Forgotten plain, where
only the damaged remain,

1569
01:29:56,757 --> 01:30:00,359
that's where I found my destiny.

1570
01:30:04,665 --> 01:30:13,706
One more lost refugee, come
with me, feel my soul-heart.

1571
01:30:13,741 --> 01:30:17,710
If you've been
seeking a new start,

1572
01:30:17,745 --> 01:30:26,719
let me be your guiding light
till the end of the night.

1573
01:30:26,754 --> 01:30:31,390
Close your eyes,
know my soul-heart,

1574
01:30:31,425 --> 01:30:35,427
keeping watch over the rampart.

1575
01:30:35,463 --> 01:30:41,433
Let me be your
shining star, leading

1576
01:30:41,469 --> 01:30:49,541
voice from afar from whoever
you were to whoever you are.

1577
01:30:52,513 --> 01:30:56,415
Feel my soul-heart now.

1578
01:30:59,620 --> 01:31:02,388
Dry all your tears.

1579
01:31:02,423 --> 01:31:07,693
I've returned after so many
years Let the creatures

1580
01:31:07,728 --> 01:31:12,664
I cherish flourish so now.

1581
01:31:15,703 --> 01:31:19,438
This is my vow.

1582
01:31:19,473 --> 01:31:23,575
Know forever my soul-heart.

1583
01:31:23,611 --> 01:31:32,618
Anyone seeking a new start,
let me be your guiding light

1584
01:31:32,653 --> 01:31:37,723
till the end of the night.

1585
01:31:37,758 --> 01:31:39,725
(GUITAR SOLO)

1586
